@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault

Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.gui

Package grouping the graphical user interface related entities
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardBlockPane
    Represents a single block (cell) of the board game
    BoardContentPane
    Represents the content of the board
    BoardPane
    This class extends the GridPane element in order to represent the game field
    CallbackFactory
    Factory class that provides callback functions for different ButtonTypes, each with the expected return value
    GameController
    Main class controlling the graphical interface during a match
    GUI
    This class represents the graphical interface of the game
    ImagePane
    This class represents an Image in JavaFX environments, the image is shown as the background of a Pane, so that its dimension can be controlled more easily
    LoginController
    Class that manages the login screen
    NotificationController
    This class handles and displays small notification windows
    PlayerBoardPane
    This class represents the Board of a single Player
    SelectPane
    This class, which extends DialogPane, allows the selection of one of the given set of options
    UrlFinder
    Utility class that composes the paths of each type of graphical element
    WindowController
    Representation of the main window of the GUI, which should be extended by the specific implementations, such as the actual game window or the login screen
